+	  fields.
+
+config CIX_DDR_LP
+	tristate "CIX Sky1 DDR low-power control"
+	depends on ARCH_CIX || COMPILE_TEST
+	depends on HAVE_ARM_SMCCC
+	depends on OF || ACPI
+	help
+	  Build the CIX Sky1 DDR low-power control driver. The vendor Device
